I don't have the RFC number handy, but there was an RFC by Paul
Mockapetris suggesting how the network information may be added
to the DNS.  The mods to get getnetby*() are similar to gethostby*().
Don't forget to supprt the linear scan still as a fallback routine
may be needed in some cases.

				Jim Bloom

